    <h3 id="examples-navbars">巡覽列實戰<!--Navbars in action--></h3>
    <div class="row bs-examples">
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-4">
            <a class="thumbnail" href="@Url.RouteUrl("BS3", new { action = "Examples", name = "navbar" })">
                @Html.LazyLoadImg(Url.Content("~/Content/AssetsBS3/examples/screenshots/navbar.jpg"), "巡覽列", "800", "600", new { @class = "lazy" })
            </a>
            <h4>巡覽列<!--Navbar--></h4>
            <p>
                超入門的範本，僅含有巡覽列與一些額外內容。
                <!--Super basic template that includes the navbar along with some additional content.-->
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-4">
            <a class="thumbnail" href="@Url.RouteUrl("BS3", new { action = "Examples", name = "navbar-static-top" })">
                @Html.LazyLoadImg(Url.Content("~/Content/AssetsBS3/examples/screenshots/navbar-static.jpg"), "靜態置頂巡覽列", "800", "600", new { @class = "lazy" })
            </a>
            <h4>靜態置頂巡覽列<!--Static top navbar--></h4>
            <p>
                超入門的範本，僅含有置頂巡覽列與一些額外內容。
                <!--Super basic template with a static top navbar along with some additional content.-->
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="clearfix visible-xs"></div>

        <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-4">
            <a class="thumbnail" href="@Url.RouteUrl("BS3", new { action = "Examples", name = "navbar-fixed-top" })">
                @Html.LazyLoadImg(Url.Content("~/Content/AssetsBS3/examples/screenshots/navbar-fixed.jpg"), "固定巡覽列", "800", "600", new { @class = "lazy" })
            </a>
            <h4>固定巡覽列<!--Fixed navbar--></h4>
            <p>
                超入門的範本，僅含有固定巡覽列與一些額外內容。
                <!--Super basic template with a fixed top navbar along with some additional content.-->
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bs-callout bs-callout-warning">
        <h4>譯者註</h4>
        <p>Bootstrap 文件中的"靜態（Static）"通常意思是固定不隨畫面滑動而移動。而"固定（Fixed）"通常意思是指元素（或容器）的位置會固定在畫面上且隨畫面滑動而移動，就像是固定在畫面上一樣。</p>
    </div>

